sequenceDiagram
    participant S as gameStore.endDay
    participant SM as staffSystem
    participant SE as settlement
    participant UI as EventCard/EventModal
    participant IP as interpolateStory

    %% —— 块 A：离职状态机每日流程 ——
    Note over S,SM: 块 A · 每日员工逻辑
    S->>SM: applyMoraleDecay(employees)
    SM-->>S: 返回更新后员工 + StaffEvent
    Note right of SM: morale 跨过 ≤20 → status='warning', warningWorkDays=0\nmorale 回升 >20 → 复位 stable
    S->>SM: advanceWarningAndResign(employees)
    Note right of SM: warning 员工 isScheduledToday → +1 否则清零\nwarningWorkDays>=6 && morale<=20 → 进 resigning
    SM-->>S: resigning 列表
    S->>SM: checkResignOrStrike(employees)
    Note right of SM: 仅保留 troublemaker 罢工（不卡 6 天）
    S->>S: 过滤 resigning / 罢工取消排班

    %% —— 块 B：老板顶班结算流程 ——
    Note over S,SE: 块 B · 顶班承载
    S->>S: 兜底：无人排班 → ownerCoverToday=true (保留 ownerFatigue+15)
    S->>SE: resolveSettlement(state, store, ..., ownerCoverToday)
    Note right of SE: effectiveCap = computeCapacity(employees)\n + (ownerCoverToday ? 70 : 0)
    SE-->>S: DailyResult（effectiveCap 含顶班加成）

    %% —— 块 C：story 渲染流程 ——
    Note over S,UI: 块 C · story 挂载
    S->>S: chooseEventOption → eventHistory 存 {story: opt.story}\nresolvedEvent 携带完整 option（含 story）
    UI->>UI: text = option.story ?? option.visibleEffect
    UI->>IP: interpolateStory(text, {name, storeName})
    Note right of IP: {name}→员工名(或"店员")；{店名}→店名\n无残留花括号
    IP-->>UI: 显示叙事文案
